{"tid":631540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英軍擔心俄國色慾誘惑","createTime":"2018-04-16T14:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T06:03:17.000Z","uid":46892,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"71129109ab30d91d090cd73e67b693f181f8f942","tid":631540,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=jl9%2FGclZ4d7fMGeX%2F4pQhcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a35b8d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英國保安專家透露，俄羅斯將派出性感女郎設下「肉彈誘惑」，對象包括英格蘭國家隊球星。<br />\n<br />\n今夏將上演世界盃決賽周，備受關注的俄羅斯足球流氓，兩年前在歐國盃期間，俄羅斯球迷與英格蘭粉絲在馬賽正面交鋒，多幕衝突畫面在電視和網絡上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n白金漢大學安全與情報中心總監基爾斯（Anthony Glees）透露：「俄羅斯女生性感、高佻、迷人，她們出盡法寶影響英格蘭的備戰，即使英格蘭在世界盃奪冠機會渺茫，但她們會透過食物落毒，甚至派出女生誘惑國腳，擾亂三獅軍團軍心。」<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯的手段有硬有軟，1名前外交官警告，身在俄羅斯的英國官員要格外小心當地女生投懷送抱，「肉彈誘惑」一直是克里姆林宮的戰術之一。<br />\n<br />\n東道主俄羅斯在A組，英格蘭則在G組，最快要到淘汰賽階段才有機會碰頭。"},{"pid":"69181d203403541810c8b09410cf5b97040dfa1b","tid":631540,"uid":46892,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://secure.i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/00789/john_terry113afp_789999c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.i.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F00789%2Fjohn_terry113afp_789999c.jpg&h=980c39c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f5e9207d7d0f8e59ee4779d50a58f1721568e7","tid":631540,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"紅雀特工 2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9d34e9ab5d6710ff158cb96ef2d0d75ab45dac","tid":631540,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69181d203403541810c8b09410cf5b97040dfa1b","tid":631540,"uid":46892,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://secure.i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/00789/john_terry113af